.ie \n(.g .ds Aq \(aq
.el .ds Aq '
.TH g-commit 1  "g-commit " 
.SH NAME
g\-commit \- Interactive guided commit with message templates
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBg\-commit\fR [\fB\-m\fR|\fB\-\-message\fR] [\fB\-b\fR|\fB\-\-body\fR] [\fB\-\-type\fR] [\fB\-\-scope\fR] [\fB\-\-no\-verify\fR] [\fB\-a\fR|\fB\-\-all\fR] [\fB\-\-amend\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Interactive guided commit with message templates
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-m\fR, \fB\-\-message\fR \fI<MESSAGE>\fR
Commit message subject (skips interactive mode)
.TP
\fB\-b\fR, \fB\-\-body\fR \fI<BODY>\fR
Commit message body
.TP
\fB\-\-type\fR \fI<TYPE>\fR
Commit type (feat, fix, docs, etc.) — skips prompt
.TP
\fB\-\-scope\fR \fI<SCOPE>\fR
Commit scope — skips prompt
.TP
\fB\-\-no\-verify\fR
Don\*(Aqt run pre\-commit hooks
.TP
\fB\-a\fR, \fB\-\-all\fR
Stage all changes before committing
.TP
\fB\-\-amend\fR
Amend the last commit
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
